David Norris pounced on his wife Dionne in the graveyard of St Nicholas Church in Southfleet . 
  The 51-year-old stabbed her repeatedly as she lay flowers on his grandmother's grave . 
  He begged her to think of their children but she 'played dead' and he was jailed for 20 years . 
  He was found guilty of attempted murder and sentenced today . 
 